title: DUSK TO DAWN VOL.02 (MIXED BY THE KRAIT)
description:
The Krait is and Upcoming Underground Trance DJ. He is an independent artist. Known For his Trance Releases namely seamless transitions series and dusk to dawn series. He has Released 4 Albums in Seamless Transition Series and 2 in Dusk to Dawn Series.


THIS ALBUM IS THE LATEST IN THE SERIES

RECOMMENDED FOR TRANCE FANS.GIVE IT A TRY... THE KRAIT WILL NOT DISAPPOINT YOU
